\nof more conventional models with large extra dimensions and 4-D portal matter.\nGenerically, the portal matter sector fields will be much lighter than the\nother KK fields in the model, so the portal matter sector has the potential to\nbe the first observable experimental signature of an extra dimension.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 23 May 2022 18:00:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 15 Jun 2022 14:26:40 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 11 Nov 2022 19:54:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-15"}
