d signals, track the inherently produced parametric features along\npropagation distance, and use method in a localisation strategy. The Bayesian\ndecomposition was found to work well for the assessment criteria mentioned\nabove. The use of these waves in the localisation method returned estimates\naccurate to within 1mm in many sensor configurations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 24 May 2022 15:48:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-20"}
