ks) over\nprior adaptation methods that assume access to large amounts of annotated\nsource data for adaptation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 24 May 2022 05:50:49 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 15 Jul 2022 09:32:28 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 22 Oct 2022 11:57:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-26"}
